    "Next, we analyze how the maximum fork length 𝐿 affects the security threshold (Figure 6).",
    "We set 𝑁 ℓ to 25.For all protocols, increasing 𝐿 reduces the security threshold.",
    "This effect becomes negligible when 𝐿 is 10 or more.Comparison to Full model.",
    "Last, we compare the results between the full model and the upper-bound model for both Colordag and Canonical-DAG (Figure 7).",
